{"tid":1203223,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"高銀潘蘇通：倘啟德商業地重推　會以個人名義競投","createTime":"2019-06-11T11:54:57.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-11T12:18:52.000Z","uid":240362,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"ffbf0da4cfce8f8e19c52ff13d0dea180ea76d69","tid":1203223,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T11:54:57.000Z","msg":"高銀金融(00530)上月以逾111億元投得的啟德舊跑道區商業地，最終未有如期在今日完成交易。該公司主席潘蘇通對結果感到「茫然、無奈」，並表示將來地皮若再次推出，會以個人名義積極參與競投。他認為，現時經濟環境短期有波動，但中長期一定會好，認為上月的中標金額好好價，下次再投地價或會更高。"},{"pid":"028258872a64613e03dd386aef9a2597add769b5","tid":1203223,"uid":46737,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T12:06:39.000Z","msg":"幾年後起好仲有冇中資美資幫你托價挨貴租<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />乜資都走曬啦"},{"pid":"854df5e968154f59a3e46851f5229f18e3d77b1d","tid":1203223,"uid":33307,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T12:08:39.000Z","msg":"扮投唔中<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5a48815d68c228545438b8824c9d1bcb16e6036c","tid":1203223,"uid":26451,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T12:17:06.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"77ff56a4d9bde30a514cdcf6dcfd27951911d3c4","tid":1203223,"uid":245441,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-11T12:18:52.000Z","msg":"潘生你天津果座摩天大樓而家起成點呀"}]}